name: CANADIAN SYLLABICS WEST-CREE Y
comment: This character has a misleading name; I used to think the opposite, but Cree writers prefer the rendering of FINAL PLUS—slightly higher than WEST-CREE FINAL Y

name: CANADIAN SYLLABICS T
comment: They render similarly, but WEST-CREE M is correct.

name: CANADIAN SYLLABICS SAYISI YI
comment: They render similarly, but this one represents HK.
